data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of our prestigious Master-Planned community, Tartesso with OWNED SOLAR and OWNED ALARM SYSTEM! This stunning single-family residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and community living. The home was just updated with new flooring (2022), extended concrete backyard patio (2022) and a home theater room!  Community offers, neighborhood parks, greenbelts, sports park with baseball fields, soccer fields, basketball, volleyball, tennis courts, splash pads, and ramadas for those amazing Arizona BBQ's.
